title: Unicorn Tape, Danish Furniture and More (The Good, the Bad, and the Whacky)
description:
On this episode of Sleep and Relax ASMR, we return with a new rendition of "The Good, the Bad, and the Whacky." We'll explore wine condoms, portable electric fireplaces, and more interesting items available on Amazon. Enjoy!

---

  • e-Flame Portable Electric Fireplace (Black): https://amzn.to/2SVi1jb 
  • Wine Condoms: https://amzn.to/2H2PYLC
  • NPW Unicorn Tape:  https://amzn.to/2VTyE0B 
  • Tvilum Danish Furniture (Diana Coffee Table):https://amzn.to/2TMi40O
